    <p>Cut For Com­pas­sion</p>
    <p>Cut or shave your hair to show sup­port for pa­tients suf­fer­ing from cancer or other chronic ill­nesses. In its fifth run, Cut For Com­pas­sion raises funds for the Com­pas­sion Sup­port Scheme, which pro­vides fi­nan­cial sup­port to ben­e­fi­cia­ries for pre­ven­tive ther­a­pies and well­ness cour­ses. This year, you can opt to cut some other comforts, such as junk food or pa­per us­age, as part of your cam­paign. Or adopt a pledge card and get your friends and fam­ily to sup­port. Or­gan­ised by Kam­pung Se­nang, a vol­un­teer-driven char­ity and ed­u­ca­tion or­gan­i­sa­tion.</p>
    <p>WHEN: To­day - Dec 16</p>
    <p>INFO: com­pas­sion.sg/ cut­for­com­pas­sion20</p>


